<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HOME</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="main.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.0.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-1ycn6IcaQQ40/MKBW2W4Rhis/DbILU74C1vSrLJxCq57o941Ym01SwNsOMqvEBFlcgUa6xLiPY/NS5R+E6ztJQ=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.8/jquery-ui.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <link href="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.8/themes/base/jquery-ui.css" rel="Stylesheet"
        type="text/css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/icons/node-js.svg" color="#5bbad5">
</head>

<body class="changeNotify">


    <div class="home-header-contaier">

        <div class="left_area">

            <div class="row">
                <a href="/" style="text-decoration: none;">
                    <h3>THÔNG <span>BÁO</span></h3>
                </a>
            </div>

        </div>

        <div class="home-header-nameProfile">
            <span class="nameProfile">HN</span>
        </div>

        <div class="right_area">
            <div class="home-header-imgProfile">
                <img src="<%=user.avatar%>" alt="" class="">
            </div>

            <br>
            <h2 class="mt-2">
                <%=user.name%>
            </h2>
            <hr class="shareHr">

            <ul>
                <a href="/info">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-user" aria-hidden="true"></i>Trang cá nhân</li>
                </a>
                <% if (auth){ %>
                    <a href="/register">
                        <li><i class="fa fa-inbox" aria-hidden="true"></i>Tạo phòng ban</li>
                    </a>
                    <% }%>
                        <a href="/logout">
                            <li class="logout-profile"><i class="fa fa-sign-out-alt" aria-hidden="true"></i>Logout</li>
                        </a>
            </ul>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="home-nav-container">

        <div class="home-nav-sidebar">
            <div class="home-nav-sidebarList">

                <div class="home-nav-imgProfile">
                    <%=user.name%>
                </div>
                <ul class="home-nav-sidebarListFeat">

                    <li>
                        <a href="/" class="home"><i class="fa fa-home"></i><span title="Trang chủ">Trang
                                chủ</span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="home-nav-categoryMessage first"><i class="fas fa-list"></i><span class="first"
                                title="Phân loại thông báo">Đơn vị</span><span
                                class="fas fa-chevron-left showList first"></span></a>

                        <nav>
                            <ul class="home-nav-listMessage">

                                <li>
                                    <a href="/phongban" class="donvi"><i class="fas fa-users"></i><span
                                            title="Đơn vị">Khoa/Phòng ban</span></a>

                                </li>

                            </ul>
                        </nav>

                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="logout-profile">

                            <a href="/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i><span>Logout</span></a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-nav-contentStatus">

            <div class="home-nav-Status">
                <div class="row row-status">

                    <div class="col-sm-8">
                        <div class="postStatus">

                            <div class="row postStatus-row">
                                <div class="share">
                                    <form action="/api/posts" method="POST" id="formCreate"
                                        enctype="multipart/form-data" class="formCreate">

                                        <div class="shareWrapper">

                                            <div class="shareTop">
                                                <img src="<%=user.avatar%>" class="shareProfileImg" id="imgProfile"
                                                    alt="">
                                                <textarea name="description" id="description" onkeyup="countChar(this)"
                                                    type="text" placeholder="What's in your mind"
                                                    class="shareInput"></textarea>

                                            </div>

                                            <hr class="shareHr">

                                            <div class="addImage-Post">
                                                <span class="">
                                                    <i class='fas fa-angle-double-down showmore '
                                                        style="font-size: 18px;"></i>
                                                </span>


                                            </div>

                                            <div class="shareBottom">
                                                <div class="title_Image">
                                                    ẢNH
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                                                    <div class="custom-file">
                                                        <label class="custom-file-label" name="labelImage"
                                                            id="labelImage" for="image_file">
                                                            Thêm ảnh vào bài viết
                                                        </label>

                                                        <input accept="image/*" type="file" name='image' id='image_file'
                                                            class="custom-file-input shareOptionText"></input>
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>

                                            </div>
                                            <div class="shareBottom">
                                                <div class="title_Image">
                                                    Link YouTube
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                                                    <div class="custom-file">


                                                        <input type="text" id="video" class="form-control"
                                                            placeholder="Thêm Link">
                                                    </div>

                                                </div>

                                            </div>
                                            <button class="shareButton" type="submit" id="createPost">Share</button>

                                    </form>
                                    <script>

                                    </script>

                                    <div class="center">

                                        <div class="ring">

                                        </div>
                                        <span class="loading">
                                            posting...
                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>


                                <div id="demo">
                                    <div class="alert alert-success">
                                        <strong>THÔNG BÁO!</strong> thêm thành công bài viết mới !!!
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>

                    </div>

                    <div class="timeline">
                        <% postTimeline.forEach(e=> {

                            %>

                            <div class="home-newFeed-container <%=e._id%>">
                                <div class="home-newFeed">

                                    <div class="home-status">

                                        <div class="home-nav-headerPost">

                                            <div class="postTopLeft">
                                                <img class="img_userPost" src="<%=e.user.avatar%>" alt="">

                                                <span class="name_userPost">
                                                    <%=e.user.name%>
                                                </span>

                                                <span class="postDate">
                                                    <%= e.timestamps %>
                                                </span>

                                                <span class="postSetting" data-id="<%= e._id %>"><i
                                                        class="fas fa-ellipsis-h"></i></span>
                                            </div>


                                            <div class="textSetting" id="<%=e._id%>">

                                                <ul>
                                                    <a href="#">
                                                        <li><i class="fa fa-user" aria-hidden="true"></i>Lưu bài
                                                            viết</li>
                                                    </a>
                                                    <a href="#">
                                                        <li><i class="fa fa-users" aria-hidden="true"></i>Chỉnh sửa
                                                            bài viết</li>
                                                    </a>

                                                    <a class="deletePost" href="#" data-id="<%= e._id %>">
                                                        <li><i class="fa fa-inbox" aria-hidden="true"></i>Xóa bài
                                                            viết</li>
                                                    </a>

                                                </ul>

                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                        <div class="home-nav-contentPost">

                                            <div class="postText">
                                                <%= e.description %>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="image-Post">

                                                <% if (e.thumbnail!='' ){%>

                                                    <img src="<%=e.thumbnail%>" alt="">

                                                    <% }%>

                                                        <% if (e.video!='' && e.thumbnail=='' ){%>

                                                            <!-- <iframe width="775.18" height="400"
                                                                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/<%=e.video%>"
                                                                title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
                                                                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
                                                                allowfullscreen></iframe> -->

                                                            <% }%>
                                            </div>



                                        </div>

                                        <hr class="shareHr">



                                        <div class="home-nav-userComment">

                                            <a href="">
                                                <span class="home-comment-post">
                                                    <img src="<%=user.avatar%>" alt="">
                                                </span>
                                            </a>

                                            <input type="text" class="content-userComment"
                                                placeholder="What's on your mind, Nguyen?">
                                        </div>

                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <% }); %>

                    </div>


                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-4">

                    <div class="home-header-container">
                        <h3>Thông báo mới</h3>
                        <a href="/notifications">Xem tất cả</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="home-sidebar-message">
                        <div class="list-group">
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start ">
                                <div class=" justify-content-between">
                                    <small><span class="home-message-userupload">[Phòng đại học]</span>
                                        <span class="home-message-dateupload"> 22-01-2021 </span></small>
                                    <h5>Thông báo đóng học phí học kì II 2021-2022</h5>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">Từ 10h00 thứ Tư ngày 13/10/2021 đến 9h00 thứ Tư ngày 26/1/2022</p>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start ">
                                <div class=" justify-content-between">
                                    <small><span class="home-message-userupload">[Phòng CTHSSV]</span>
                                        <span class="home-message-dateupload"> 22-01-2021 </span></small>
                                    <h5>Kế hoạch xét công nhận tốt nghiệp đợt tháng 01/2022</h5>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">Sinh viên xem chi tiết trong thông báo.</p>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action flex-column align-items-start ">
                                <div class=" justify-content-between">
                                    <h5 class="mb-1">[Phòng đại học]
                                        <span class="home-sidebar-dateupload">03-02-2021</span>
                                    </h5>
                                    <small><span class="home-message-userupload">[Phòng đại học]</span>
                                        <span class="home-message-dateupload"> 22-01-2021 </span></small>
                                    <h5>Lịch thi và danh sách thi cuối kỳ HKdt1/2021-2022</h5>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mb-1">Sinh viên xem chi tiết Lịch thi và danh sách thi cuối kỳ
                                    HKdt1/2021-2022 trong file đính kèm.</p>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class='datepicker'>
                        <div class="datepicker-header"></div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>